posts.subject: Welcome
posts.body:
The premise of this board is to pool ideas for anons in need. If you have tips on staying anonymous from (((them))), please share.

A few starting tips:

Always use a VPN for your more edgy side. They usually cost shekels, and the free ones can be compromised.
Purchase a VPN with bitcoin.
Always use TOR for 8chan, 4chan, etc.
Use Pale Moon with anti-tracking addons for regular browsing.
Avoid mobile browsing of edgy sites at all times. Mobile browsers are easily tracked.

Remember, on this board, there are no stupid questions.

(source of my last comment for those about to call me JIDF: https://thegreateststorynevertold.tv/as-many-as-150000-jews-served-in-hitlers-military/)
